### Test Workflows API - Phase 2
### Workflow Engine Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@acme.local",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 2. Get all workflows
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get workflow by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get workflow steps
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/1/steps
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get available approvers
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/approvers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Create new workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phê duyệt báo cáo",
  "description": "Quy trình phê duyệt báo cáo định kỳ",
  "document_type_id": 7
}

### 7. Update workflow
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phê duyệt báo cáo (Updated)",
  "description": "Quy trình phê duyệt báo cáo định kỳ - đã cập nhật",
  "is_active": true
}

### 8. Add step to workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/4/steps
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "step_name": "Phê duyệt của Trưởng phòng",
  "approver_type": "role",
  "approver_id": 1,
  "due_in_days": 3,
  "is_required": true
}

### 9. Update workflow step
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/steps/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "step_name": "Phê duyệt của Giám đốc (Updated)",
  "due_in_days": 5
}

### 10. Reorder workflow steps
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/1/steps/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "steps": [
    { "id": 1, "step_order": 1 },
    { "id": 2, "step_order": 2 }
  ]
}

### 11. Delete workflow step
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workflows/steps/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Delete workflow
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workflows/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Summary:
# ✅ Workflows CRUD
# ✅ Workflow steps management
# ✅ Reorder steps
# ✅ Get available approvers
